      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; experimental sample characterisation requirements deferred to higher MRL.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2 the test-samples factor is not required to be formally assessed. The FDA pump experimental data used for validation were collected under a published protocol with documented fluid batch characterisation; no additional sample assessment obligation applies at this risk level."
